STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Rashaun A. FENTRESS, a/k/a Shawn B. Fentres, Rashuan A. Fentress, Rashaun Ban, Zeus Fentress, Rashaun Zuse, and Allan Francis, Defendant-Petitioner. C-1038 September Term 2018
082405 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001720-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
